    "summary": "Leading a research group focused on information-processing in structured elastic materials. Highlight applications include the pursuit of zero power wake-up word detection, under the ERC-funded project INFOPASS. We combine a fundamental interest to understand the limits and principles that govern information processing in physical systems with an applied drive to answer the low-energy and ubiquitous computing needs of the future. To achieve these goals, we combine advanced simulation and design methods with cleanroom fabrication techniques.",
